---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 56-57
By: Hermes
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Separation-Sin=God Alone Is Good
  - Beauty-Peace=Beauty=The Doctrine of the Archetypes
---
The Good cannot be in things that come into being, but only in that which is
without beginning.

Yet as participation in all (the ideal archetypes of things) is distributed
in the world of matter, so also participation in the Good. And in this way
the Kosmos too is good.
